descriptionHtml:
a large castle full of knights for you to fight, There are six allies there to help you.


To get to the castle, read the book in your inventory. 
It is located in its own worldspace.


If for some reason the options dont appear, drop the book then read it again.
To leave, fast travel out. If enough people enjoy the mod, I will expand it and include a normal exit.
author: DeadDremora
